  img(src="/assets/hotelhenry.jpg").hero-image
  hr
  .location-container
    .location-info
      h3 Hotel Henry
      p Hotel Henry is located at #[a(href="https://goo.gl/maps/VFv2mDxGjto") 444 Forest Ave, Buffalo NY, 14213]. The entrance is off of Rockwell Rd. Free valet service will be provided.
      h3 Coming From Cuba
      p If you are coming from Cuba, here is our recommended set of directions.
      ol
        li Take 16 N to 400 N
        li Take 400 N to I-190 N
        li Take I-190 N to NY-198 Scajauda Expressway
        li Take the Grant St exit
        li Turn left onto Letchworth Rd
        li Continue onto Rockwell Rd
        li Look for sign for Hotel Henry entrance on right
